---
title: Salmon and Shrimp in Lemon-Caper Cream Sauce with Garlicky Roasted Potatoes
description: This creamy caper-Dijon sauce adds a luxurious touch to salmon and shrimp. Roasted potatoes tossed in garlic-butter are perfect for sopping up all that saucy goodness!
